MODEL S Order Now on Tokopedia [vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1581106617684{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}”][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Pricing and options will be finalised as delivery approaches. You will be notified to complete your order when final pricing and options are published. Until then, your order will be considered a pre-order that you may cancel with a full refund.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” content_placement=”top” css=”.vc_custom_1650454573026{padding-top: 30px !important;}”][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Interior of the Future

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=”7489″ img_size=”full”][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator color=”white” el_width=”70″][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” css=”.vc_custom_1650510559256{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-color: #000000 !important;}”][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]

Interior Features

Audio and Media

  1. Premium 22-speaker audio with Active Road Noise Reduction
  2. Multi-device music and media over Bluetooth®
  3. 17” centre display, 12.3” driver’s display, and 8” second row display
  4. Gaming computer with 10 teraflops of processing power
  5. Wireless controller compatibility

 

Comfort

  1. Heated seats for every passenger, heated steering and heated windshield
  2. Ventilated front seating
  3. Tri-zone Airwave cabin conditioning
  4. HEPA air filtration system
  5. Custom driver profiles with automatic easy-entry and exit
  6. Ambient lighting
  7. Tinted glass roof
  8. Ultraviolet and infrared protection on all glass

 

Convenience

  1. Front centre console with sliding cup holders and storage
  2. Second row stowable centre armrest with integrated storage and wireless charging
  3. Automatic opening and closing rear liftgate
  4. Auto dimming, power folding, heated side mirrors
  5. 28 ft³ of cargo space and secure front boot
  6. Wireless and USB-C fast charging for every passenger
  7. Location-aware automatic garage door opener
  8. Phone Key

 

Premium Connectivity, 1 year complimentary

  1. Live traffic visualization
  2. Satellite-View Maps
  3. Video Streaming with access to Netflix, Youtube, Twitch, and more
  4. Caraoke
  5. Music Streaming
  6. Internet Browser
    *New features that become available after delivery may be subject to additional charges.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1581106617684{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}”][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Plaid Upgrades

  1. Acceleration from 0-60 mph: 1.99s
  2. 1020 horsepower
  3. Three high performance drive units
  4. Carbon-sleeved rotors
  5. Torque vectoring
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Enhanced Autopilot

  1. Navigate on Autopilot
  2. Auto Lane Change
  3. Autopark
  4. Summon
  5. Smart Summon
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Full Self-Driving Capability

  1. All functionality of Basic Autopilot and Enhanced Autopilot
  2. Traffic Light and Stop Sign Control

Upcoming:

  1. Autosteer on city streets
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The currently enabled features require active driver supervision and do not make the vehicle autonomous. Some features require turn signals and are limited in range. The activation and use of these features are dependent on achieving reliability far in excess of human drivers as demonstrated by billions of miles of experience, as well as regulatory approval, which may take longer in some jurisdictions. As these self-driving features evolve, your car will be continuously upgraded through over-the-air software updates. Please read the Owner’s Manual for further information.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1581106617684{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}”][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]
Plaid

Beyond Ludicrous

With the most power and quickest acceleration of any SUV, Model X Plaid is the highest performing SUV ever built. All Model X powertrains, with updated battery architecture, can deliver instant torque at any speed.With the most power and quickest acceleration of any SUV, Model X Plaid is the highest performing SUV ever built. All Model X powertrains, with updated battery architecture, can deliver instant torque at any speed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1581106617684{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}”][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Utility

Relentless Performance

Staggered, performance wheels and tires keep the car planted and help transfer maximum power down to the road.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1581106617684{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}”][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Exterior

Designed for Efficiency

With a drag coefficient of just .208 Cd, the lowest on the planet, Model S is built for speed, endurance and range. Improved aerodynamics and a wider chassis offer more responsive performance so you can take corners quicker and with more confidence.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1579114326284{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Optimized Aerodynamics

Attention to detail on all exterior surfaces makes Model S the most aerodynamic production car on Earth.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1650521228720{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Refined Styling

An iconic silhouette meets refreshed, elegant proportions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1650521148559{padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column css=”.vc_custom_1650521197027{padding-top: 30px !important;}”][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Range
Go Anywhere

Travel farther on a single charge than any other electric vehicle—and keep going with access to 30,000+ Superchargers globally. By combining up to 405 miles of estimated range with Tesla fast charging technology, you’ll spend less time charging and even more time on the road.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1650521228720{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Safety
High Impact Protection

Model S is built from the ground up as an electric vehicle, with a high-strength architecture and floor-mounted battery pack for incredible occupant protection and low rollover risk. Every new Model S includes Tesla’s latest active safety features, such as Automatic Emergency Braking, at no extra cost.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1650521148559{padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column css=”.vc_custom_1650521197027{padding-top: 30px !important;}”][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Autopilot
Future of Driving

Autopilot enables your car to steer, accelerate and brake automatically within its lane under your active supervision, assisting with the most burdensome parts of driving. With over-the-air software updates, the latest enhancements are available instantly.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row et_full_width=”true” et_row_padding=”true” et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1650521228720{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}”][vc_column][vc_row_inner et_column_align=”align-center” content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″]

[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][vc_column_text]

Features

Full Self-Driving capability introduces additional features and improves existing functionality to make your car more capable over time

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space]
